  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survival Gameplay</strong> </h2>Defend your home from endless waves of enemies, each more challenging than the last.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/152f1407d58e1964f723a66aa5b68a32.poster.avif?t=1726043779\" width=598 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/152f1407d58e1964f723a66aa5b68a32.webm?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/152f1407d58e1964f723a66aa5b68a32.mp4?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Resource Management</strong> </h2>Collect coins to buy food and increase the population to place your units.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/c1e0208d2faec94e329dd3c9c08370db.poster.avif?t=1726043779\" width=598 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/c1e0208d2faec94e329dd3c9c08370db.webm?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/c1e0208d2faec94e329dd3c9c08370db.mp4?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike Elements</strong></h2>Each time you level up, choose from one of three unique power-ups to enhance your abilities and customize your playstyle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/28501042e74170060e02a3ee2b1e9cdc.poster.avif?t=1726043779\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/28501042e74170060e02a3ee2b1e9cdc.webm?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/28501042e74170060e02a3ee2b1e9cdc.mp4?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse Units</strong></h2>Unlock and use 13 unique units to defend your home. You can move these units in the preparation phase ensuring your defenses remain strong after every wave.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/5e72291e583dd305939994a2e84ecd49.poster.avif?t=1726043779\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/5e72291e583dd305939994a2e84ecd49.webm?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/5e72291e583dd305939994a2e84ecd49.mp4?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Early Access</strong> </h2>The game offers 4-5 hours of gameplay to unlock all the units, but you can keep playing endlessly to chase the high score. Join us in the development journey! Your feedback will be crucial as we add new features, balanced gameplay, and improve the overall experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Note From The Dev</strong></h2><br>Last Home is a labor of love developed by a solo developer, marking my first foray into the world of game development. This project represents hours of dedication, creativity, and passion. Your support means the world to me, and I hope you enjoy the experience as much as I enjoyed creating it. Thank you for joining me on this incredible journey.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survival Gameplay</strong> </h2>Defend your home from endless waves of enemies, each more challenging than the last.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/152f1407d58e1964f723a66aa5b68a32.poster.avif?t=1726043779\" width=598 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/152f1407d58e1964f723a66aa5b68a32.webm?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/152f1407d58e1964f723a66aa5b68a32.mp4?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Resource Management</strong> </h2>Collect coins to buy food and increase the population to place your units.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/c1e0208d2faec94e329dd3c9c08370db.poster.avif?t=1726043779\" width=598 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/c1e0208d2faec94e329dd3c9c08370db.webm?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/c1e0208d2faec94e329dd3c9c08370db.mp4?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Roguelike Elements</strong></h2>Each time you level up, choose from one of three unique power-ups to enhance your abilities and customize your playstyle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/28501042e74170060e02a3ee2b1e9cdc.poster.avif?t=1726043779\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/28501042e74170060e02a3ee2b1e9cdc.webm?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/28501042e74170060e02a3ee2b1e9cdc.mp4?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse Units</strong></h2>Unlock and use 13 unique units to defend your home. You can move these units in the preparation phase ensuring your defenses remain strong after every wave.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/5e72291e583dd305939994a2e84ecd49.poster.avif?t=1726043779\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/5e72291e583dd305939994a2e84ecd49.webm?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090600/extras/5e72291e583dd305939994a2e84ecd49.mp4?t=1726043779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Early Access</strong> </h2>The game offers 4-5 hours of gameplay to unlock all the units, but you can keep playing endlessly to chase the high score. Join us in the development journey! Your feedback will be crucial as we add new features, balanced gameplay, and improve the overall experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Note From The Dev</strong></h2><br>Last Home is a labor of love developed by a solo developer, marking my first foray into the world of game development. This project represents hours of dedication, creativity, and passion. Your support means the world to me, and I hope you enjoy the experience as much as I enjoyed creating it. Thank you for joining me on this incredible journey.",
